{"title":"linux下nginx的安装和配置","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:19.007Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/linux下nginx的安装和配置","updated":"2023-07-28T09:12:39.617Z","content":"<h2 id=\"一、简单安装\"><strong>一、简单安装</strong><a title=\"#一、简单安装\" href=\"#一、简单安装\"></a></h2>\n<p>直接</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo apt install nginx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>然后</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">nginx <span class=\"literal\">-t</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>测试并找出配置文件</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">nginx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>启动服务即可<br>\nnginx的配置文件在<code>/etc/nginx/nginx.conf</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"二、手动安装nginx\">二、手动安装nginx<a title=\"#二、手动安装nginx\" href=\"#二、手动安装nginx\"></a></h2>\n<p><strong>1、安装prce，让 Nginx 支持 Rewrite 功能。</strong><br>\nprce的网址<a href=\"https://sourceforge.net/projects/pcre/\" target=\"_blank\">https://sourceforge.net/projects/pcre/</a></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">wget</span> https://nchc.dl.sourceforge.net/project/pcre/pcre/<span class=\"number\">8.35</span>/pcre<span class=\"literal\">-8</span>.<span class=\"number\">35</span>.tar.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/27a3b8b3efaf419eb2f349dbbf9d2583.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n解压到本地，并进入目录</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">./configure</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/123019b64bd54aa7ad2e4fe073b8d444.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n防止权限问题，用root权限执行安装</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo make&amp;&amp;make install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/46f0e5f1f19c4102a0e9123280b6f2c2.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n此时终端输入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pcre<span class=\"literal\">-config</span> <span class=\"literal\">--version</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>弹出版本提示，即为成功<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/d1f691a6f6264974b310b362a9431b78.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<strong>2、安装openssl</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo apt install openssl</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>3、<a href=\"https://nginx.org/en/download.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>下载nginx</strong>【https://nginx.org/en/download.html】</a></p>\n<p>下载稳定版<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/569b5f61cd694a0db051cc375a568ffa.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"!在这里插入图片描述(https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/ffe6ca33d02943d88f013252fd7f21bf.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_1\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>解压到本地</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/21b1263235094e9a9a073dddb50c1781.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>此时进入nginx目录，在nginx目录下执行</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">./configure</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>![在这里插入图片描述](<a href=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/4bb8b305e0c34f34b38c1b67c8b30f46.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16!%5B%E5%9C%A8%E8%BF%99%E9%87%8C%E6%8F%92%E5%85%A5%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E6%8F%8F%E8%BF%B0%5D(https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/a713ee905f9f4c56ae78156659072a9c.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16)\" target=\"_blank\">https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/4bb8b305e0c34f34b38c1b67c8b30f46.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16![在这里插入图片描述](https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/a713ee905f9f4c56ae78156659072a9c.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16)</a></p>\n<p>然后</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">make</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo make install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/3c7268fadafb424299c0d30b9586dab5.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/5254c5d5839449dca91d42db3c34ae58.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>最后输入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">nginx <span class=\"literal\">-V</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>查看版本信息<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/69e801104d664a36ab5386927afc27ea.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n此时输入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo nginx <span class=\"literal\">-t</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>测试nginx配置文件<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/9c4e9cddc8b1448e948a0615a667e9c2.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n显示nginx配置正常<br>\n以后配置nginx，只需修改这个<code>/etc/nginx/nginx.conf</code>文件即可<br>\n这里我修改了站点的目录和监听端口<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/f87be4bf06464ac6a797d7a206ddb118.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n站点路径下放了一些网页文件<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/0a76685999164e888b6b23b7975e521c.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n终端输入<code>nginx</code>启动服务<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/5ad5262d853e4fcb97261b1da192750f.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>此时打开浏览器，访问<code>localhost:81</code></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/03b9451c93264576afac1fea9d83a3eb.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n已经成功加载了我放的网页文件，配置成功</p>\n<p>nginx的常用命令</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">nginx <span class=\"literal\">-s</span> reload              <span class=\"comment\"># 重新载入配置文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">nginx <span class=\"literal\">-s</span> reopen            <span class=\"comment\"># 重启 Nginx</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">nginx <span class=\"literal\">-s</span> stop                <span class=\"comment\"># 停止 Nginx</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","prev":{"title":"linux下编译安装stellar区块链","link":"2023/07/28/linux下编译安装stellar区块链"},"next":{"title":"Linux配置ssh免密登陆","link":"2023/07/28/Linux配置ssh免密登陆"},"plink":"http://glj520.tk/2023/07/28/linux下nginx的安装和配置/","toc":[{"id":"一、简单安装","title":"一、简单安装","index":"1"},{"id":"二、手动安装nginx","title":"二、手动安装nginx","index":"2"}],"reading_time":"777 字约 5 分钟"}